{
  "title": "AD #6 · Government in the Economy (Path B)",
  "lessons": [
    {
      "translation": "Claire 说政府应介入保护消费者，Andrew 说政府应退让让企业发展。",
      "phrases": ["Claire says", "the government should step in", "to protect consumers,", "Andrew says", "it should step aside", "so business can grow."],
      "zhPhrases": ["Claire 说", "政府应该介入", "以保护消费者，", "Andrew 说", "政府应该退让，", "让企业得以发展。"]
    },
    {
      "translation": "我认为两种观点都跳过了让任何一方真正成立的东西。",
      "phrases": ["I think", "both views skip over", "what actually makes", "either side possible."],
      "zhPhrases": ["我认为", "两种观点都跳过了", "真正让", "任何一方成立的东西。"]
